work.work-title: N°85 I believe in one God

credit.credit-words: N°85 I believe in one God

lyric.name: part1verse1
lyric.text: ti ch'eshmarit'i, ghvtisagan ch'eshmart'isa shobili da araqmnili ertar

lyric.name: part1verse1
lyric.text: chvenisa tskhovrebisatvis gardamokhda zetsit da khortsni sheiskhna sulisagan ts'midi

lyric.name: part1verse1
lyric.text: oelisa p'ilat'esze da ivno da daepla da aghsdga mesamesa dghe

lyric.name: part1verse1
lyric.text: kvalad momaval ars didebit gansjad tskhovelta da mkvdar-

lyric.name: part1verse1
lyric.text: tskhovelsmq'opeli, romeli mamisagan gamovals, mamisa tana da dzisa ta
